---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';

const title = `A Brief Interrogation of ${SITE_TITLE}`
---

<!doctype HTML>
<html>
    <head>
        <BaseHead title={title} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
        <style>
            main {
				width: 960px;
			}
			main h3 span {
				text-shadow: 3px 3px 10px black;
			}
            ul, li {
				margin-top: 0px;
			}
			ul li {
                list-style-type: none;
			}
			ul li a {
				display: block;
			}
			ul li p {
                line-height: 30px;
				margin-bottom: 10px;
			}
            .inner-list li {
                margin-top: 10px;
                margin-bottom: 0px;
                list-style-type: disc;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <Header />
        <main>
            <ul>
                <div class="special-box">
                    <h3 class="center-text">üóÇÔ∏è <i>A Brief Interrogation of Grayvox</i> üóÇÔ∏è</h3>
                    <br>
                    <li id="question-one">
                        <h4>What's with the name?</h4>
                        <p>
                            I always wanted my username to involve 'Gray' or at least a wolf. After a ton of brainstorming, I came up with this.
                        </p>
                        <br>
                        Other name ideas were:
                        <ul class="inner-list">
                            <li>HowlingGray</li>
                            <li>SystemGray</li>
                            <li>VoxelWolf</li>
                            <li>GraySystems</li>
                            <li>DevByGray</li>
                        </ul>
                        <br>
                        Still hate that last one...
                    </li>
                    <li id="question-two">
                        <h4>Why a wolf?</h4>
                        <p>
                            I could be cheesy and say it's because they're "misunderstood", but I like being original.
                            Put simply, I love wolves. Beautiful, intelligent, a bit scary... and yes, misunderstood.
                            Though I do have a lot in common with them; They're extremely social creatures (unlike me), 
                            do well in packs (unlike me)... wait a minute-
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li id="question-three">
                        <h4>What sort of work do you do?</h4>
                        <p>
                            Yes.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            ...A lot of stuff, put simply. Whatever comes to mind, whatever I fancy at the time. 
                            I code stuff, write stories, draw stuff, design games, produce ideas upon ideas upon ideas 
                            upon... well, you get the idea.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li id="question-four">
                        <h4>What sort of computer do you have?</h4>
                        <p>
                            I built it myself, and will probably continue to do that every single time I need a new 
                            computer. If you're curious about the specs:
                        </p>
                        <br>
                        <ul>
                            <li><b>CPU:</b> Intel i7-13700K</li>
                            <li><b>GPU:</b> GeForce RTX 3060 12GB</li>
                            <li><b>RAM:</b> 32GB DDR5</li>
                            <li><b>Hard Drive 1:</b> Samsung 990 EVO 1TB SSD</li>
                            <li><b>Motherboard:</b> MSI Z790-A PRO MAX WIFI</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li id="question-five">
                        <h4>What software do you use?</h4>
                        <p>
                            I try a lot of different stuff honestly, meaning this is subject to change and I may or may not
                            forget to update it enough:
                        </p>
                        <br>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                <b>OS:</b> Windows 11 with WSL (running Ubuntu)
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <b>Code Editor:</b> VS Code (for everything but Java) and IntelliJ IDEA (for Java and 
                                JVM stuff)
                            </li>
                            <li><b>Game Engine:</b> Godot Engine</li>
                            <li><b>Pixel Art and Animation:</b> Aseprite</li>
                            <li><b>Sketching and General Art:</b> Krita</li>
                            <li><b>3D Modeling:</b> Blender and Material Maker</li>
                            <li><b>Recording and Streaming:</b> OBS Studio</li>
                            <li><b>Video Editing:</b> DaVinci Resolve</li>
                            <li><b>Photo Editing:</b> Figma (for thumbnail design), and GIMP (for photo editing)</li>
                            <li><b>Workspace and Note Taking:</b> Notion</li>
                            <li><b>To Do List:</b> TickTick</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </div>
            </ul>
        </main>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>

